R-7v11qNg&oe=6731FB49"}, {"file_name": "CycleBar- Home.png", "id": "522956006795209", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_522956013461875_8093803523125335619_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=11ExweajYfcQ7kNvgGJF3jE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBqyQa5I8GFn6bVFhTFZLRFutP8Uodc8i03a_2B9X6ltA&oe=6731FBBB"}, {"file_name": "PB-Callibration.png", "id": "1936493886796191", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982629_1936493890129524_3100247740643681336_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ialf4h_Dd98Q7kNvgGB6ipk&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBbO07ZbCYXnP7DdPrg5zIaOH6GLIejVbPoS2ijRos3vA&oe=6731DF97"}, {"file_name": "CB Screenshot 02.png", "id": "7985742398145636", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974859_7985742404812302_4671278461729422000_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mB9McnwGk1YQ7kNvgFVj_Gt&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAwY7f58q2fZ0DKMKJibDZ8AdB-2w_6Q9wsASkPn-nNGg&oe=6731EE0D"}, {"file_name": "CycleBar- Classes.png", "id": "485640274332590", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75269591_485640277665923_6852489760100270909_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vP5HFBUoBXEQ7kNvgHUrVPf&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCiZf4KcBuatgrFEyDTMeuVn91Zwri7doy2kIWnPKguyw&oe=6731F81C"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CB - Cover - Landscape.png", "id": "479642521355102", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974834_479642524688435_7065933209497930161_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pup_yf5ewCgQ7kNvgE9m2TS&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBu9AhD4OaJ193ztxOHD7j1aGPLoKFnXdD12zR_VAgRWQ&oe=6731D543"}, "display_name": "CycleBar", "keywords": ["fitness", "health", "cycling", "spin", "cardio"], "long_description": "Revitalize your fitness routine with CycleBar on Meta Quest! As the largest spin brand in the U.S., CycleBar delivers an unparalleled indoor cycling experience that combines the thrill of high-energy workouts with the innovation of virtual reality. Whether you're a seasoned cyclist or new to the world of spinning, our app offers a captivating and personalized journey designed to elevate your performance and keep you inspired.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **Immersive VR Rides:** Clip into the first indoor cycling VR app on the Quest and feel the rush of riding with top instructors and fellow cyclists from around the world.\n\n- **Expert Instructors:** Ride alongside professional trainers who motivate and guide you through every pedal stroke, ensuring an engaging and effective workout.\n\n- **Variety of Classes:** Choose from a wide range of rides, including high-intensity interval training (HIIT), endurance rides, themed sessions, and more.\n\n- **Personalized Experience:** Customize your workouts to match your fitness goals, with options to adjust intensity and duration for a tailored ride.\n\nEmbark on an exciting journey to fitness with CycleBar on Meta Quest. Discover the power of movement, connect with a supportive community, and transform your ride into an unforgettable experience. Your adventure starts here\u2014get ready to ride!\n{381239874674871}", "short_description": "CycleBar is the first indoor cycling app on Meta Quest! Rock Your Ride with the largest indoor cycling brand in the U.S. Whether you're a VR enthusiast or a cycling lover, our app offers exhilarating rides led by top instructors, designed to boost your endurance, strength, and motivation. Join a vibrant community, track your progress, and transform your fitness journey with CycleBar's cutting-edge virtual reality experience. Get ready to ride like never before!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xponential.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.xponential.com